<hymn_number>156</hymn_number>
<title>Thihna Jordan</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungkhamna ka chanpih,
 Buoina tamtak ka thawkpih haw;
 Thihna Jordan gal ei kaihsan tau ie,
 Khat khata chiehin;
 A nung u-ah lungkham gimthei albang ka vai.

[V2]
 Damlai gamgaw-ah bangtin ka vakviel dem?
 Van Lili pak khawpi hawiha tatte;
 Lung guola leng hawn,
 Ka maban gamgaw hi haksa diekin a hihlang.

[V3]
 2. Gamgaw ka pelhma chun,
 Buoina tamtak tuok ding ka hi;
 Lungkhamna dang hungtung ding le tua
 Tungsa haw hile,
 Van kipahna'n khal tuibang in a hihnem thei

[V4]
 3. Gamgaw ka fan lai hin,
 Nunglam, malam ka enviela;
 Mipi maua um a tam ie, lungkham,
 Thavai aw gi tawh:
 Van kipahna mulo in tamtak a liem tau.

[V5]
 Kumsawt gam nasem dingin ei zawl zaw tau,
 Van Lili pak khawpi hawiha leng ding;
 In na sunga hin,
 Mithi lak ah van hinna thu hi gen zaw tang ka.

[V6]
 4. Khawvel na chung a gik ,
 Thihnan a tha ahun zakkhum;
 Gawtmun meikhu gim na nam zo ta ie,
 Na deihguol bawldi'n;
 Lopina limhaw hin ka thagau zawl ta ki'n.</lyrics>
</song>